ordered_victim_rescue.condition: No injured individuals reported. Rescue efforts will focus on evacuation of occupants with no priority level assigned.

action_details: Given the low fire severity and lack of injured individuals, prioritize thorough ventilation of the area to reduce smoke and heat. Then, conduct a structural assessment to identify any vulnerabilities or potential hazards within the building. Adjust rescue strategies accordingly by creating temporary support systems if necessary. Meanwhile, suppress the fire using a combination of extinguishing tools as outlined in the stop_fire_strategy.
